{"tid":2187172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Carousell 中伏記","createTime":"2020-09-03T12:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T14:22:25.000Z","uid":374111,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7e89518a979260afa1feea0fe5f51dd22c6d9c7f","tid":2187172,"uid":374111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:46:57.000Z","msg":"早排係carousell 買咗2本kenko卡簿<br />\n因為係街搵咗好耐好耐都冇2*8既size  就焗住上carousell 買<br />\n點知就中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n首先我一開波就問個2本卡簿係咪全新 店主答係 咁我就拿拿林要咗啦 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a3vtcda.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa3vtcda.png&h=21d099e3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n後尾過幾日佢就同我講一本係「全新」一本係插過卡但係「新淨」既 問我ok唔ok <br />\n咁我都信佢照要啦 因為係街真係搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jojmxd7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJojmxd7.png&h=a0128e31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n點知琴日收到既「全新」同「新淨」係咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EsAQqzF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEsAQqzF.png&h=6b05a0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q4BPF73.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq4BPF73.png&h=eed31365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WiEqes3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWiEqes3.jpg&h=fcd02c5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2本啲邊都係發黃同積曬塵 太多相廢事逐張post <br />\n跟住我用濕紙巾抹一抹係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reMoLAN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreMoLAN.jpg&h=51fb5e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n後尾同返佢講 佢咁覆我<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PyyRUu0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPyyRUu0.png&h=cbbc465c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ABCOWJm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FABCOWJm.png&h=7093a74a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJyeSgH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJyeSgH.png&h=9cef3d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dW68cgH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdW68cgH.png&h=58bc3e26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NiEJLBJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNiEJLBJ.png&h=7bff5d00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我知佢一定唔會肯退錢 但問下大家遇到咁既情況接唔接受到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋真係我有潔癖同完美主義者係我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\nBtw 本卡簿155/本 我買咗2本 佢平咗20蚊俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b5b6479ad962dab155e668e8e821fe5a862ba3d","tid":2187172,"uid":2546,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:49:37.000Z","msg":"的確無用過可以叫做全新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係無expect到放咁耐黃哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7435112f32beedd78c3476219187f27fe5f88dad","tid":2187172,"uid":294238,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:50:37.000Z","msg":"全新同污糟冇衝突嘅，你一係當面驗屍先，你情我願。賊過興兵就無謂"},{"pid":"85325a320d5d5a1f50b03af91caec199335ebb3b","tid":2187172,"uid":60279,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:51:32.000Z","msg":"你都搵唔到全新 反而覺得佢有全新？<br />\nbtw未買無叫人影相 怪得邊個<br />\n<br />\n幾十當上左一堂啦"},{"pid":"46796c2b8b5075a428f7dae45d3559b780c057b6","tid":2187172,"uid":294447,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:51:52.000Z","msg":"咁又的確係全新嘅<br />\n但咁樣嘅態度 寫埋千字文 我係買家唔會幫襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5826a504ca7381eb3406dc6138755999961e2d1","tid":2187172,"uid":374111,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6b5b6479ad962dab155e668e8e821fe5a862ba3d","tid":2187172,"uid":2546,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:49:37.000Z","msg":"的確無用過可以叫做全新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係無expect到放咁耐黃哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:52:01.000Z","msg":"我接受唔到鋪曬塵仲要係抹出黎係黑色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲發黃位仲要抹唔甩"},{"pid":"aaee7f601bf5f9300fd868660537831969d46512","tid":2187172,"uid":159313,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:52:17.000Z","msg":"收到貨算你好彩啦仲咁多嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d16a61eccc4f5d6e40849aa827ce46929e1b81","tid":2187172,"uid":226739,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:53:33.000Z","msg":"撐樓主<br />\n呢d 唔叫「全新」，呢d 叫「放咗好耐冇用過」<br />\n兩樣嘢嚟"},{"pid":"c2d9e7468c6e680046e269cd3fe11de9f3dd8aea","tid":2187172,"uid":226739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:54:16.000Z","msg":"可以叫9成9 新， 但唔係全新"},{"pid":"d86e043179ee0e89da6c23f2caab360294b08951","tid":2187172,"uid":374111,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7435112f32beedd78c3476219187f27fe5f88dad","tid":2187172,"uid":294238,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:50:37.000Z","msg":"全新同污糟冇衝突嘅，你一係當面驗屍先，你情我願。賊過興兵就無謂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:54:57.000Z","msg":"佢唔俾面交啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我有件未用過全新既野係咁既狀態 <br />\n我唔會好意思賣俾人 所以冇諗過會有人好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73deee2dd795a1bf8862ea0ce3077de965aa9ba0","tid":2187172,"uid":374111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaee7f601bf5f9300fd868660537831969d4651