ts/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw後尾係官網見到有 但間野係印尼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96d9b962f3bbef86aaf10d45af91e59d43af44a6","tid":2187172,"uid":374111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cd3af7ecc7504354a16d23b90afb8c2d22ee394","tid":2187172,"uid":274722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:56:35.000Z","msg":"唔熟本簿，但本簿係咪出左好<br />\n<br />\n咁佢全新但擺係櫃3，5年舖塵黃哂都合理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"我都唔係太清楚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我係奇趣見到有 <br />\n不過唔係我想要既size"},{"pid":"3b955ae7715500e2c38a683f735d9993bc35b036","tid":2187172,"uid":374111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:02:11.000Z","msg":"Btw 開post其中一個原因係 <br />\n佢間野有超多好評 個個都俾5分咁制<br />\n我就係因為見到咁先即刻買 結果中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想提下大家下次買野見到好評多都唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a80057a828799b389c493945780334882b8bf41","tid":2187172,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"又要買二手又要做驗c官<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同之前個on9連登仔買display 屌人會唔會比垃圾卡佢有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb810d5898614db17fe993a06bb85343a57fe8e","tid":2187172,"uid":110314,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8a80057a828799b389c493945780334882b8bf41","tid":2187172,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T13:02:49.000Z","msg":"又要買二手又要做驗c官<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同之前個on9連登仔買display 屌人會唔會比垃圾卡佢有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime